HEADWORD: Durableness
<hw>Du"ra*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Power of lasting, enduring,
or resisting; durability.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>durableness</qex> of the metal that supports it.</q>
